// Baked reference-image data for the mountain splash scene.
//
// This is NOT procedurally generated — it's a real 24-bit RGB render of
// the reference mountain artwork (420x70, row-major, base64-encoded,
// decoded at runtime with Node's built-in Buffer — no extra dependency).
// Same exact colors/gradient/scale as the original capture — only two
// spots were patched, both by extending a clean neighboring row's color
// rather than resizing anything (so the overall image scale is untouched):
// the decorative top border stripe (rows 0-2) is blanked to plain sky,
// and the blurry baked-in mascot silhouette (rows 41-69, cols 5-70) is
// replaced with flat ground color so mountainScene() can draw its own
// crisp mascot and its own stars on top of pure terrain instead.
export const MOUNTAIN_GRID_W = 420;
export const MOUNTAIN_GRID_H = 70;
export const MOUNTAIN_GRID_B64 = '';
